headline: Fastenal Company Announces Two-For-One Stock Split
summary: WINONA, Minn., April 23, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq:FAST) ('Fastenal', the 'Company', 'we', 'our', or 'us') announced today that its board of directors approved a two-for-one stock split of the Company's outstanding common stock to be effected through an amendment to the Company's Restated Articles of Incorporation (the 'Amendment'). The Amendment will also effect a proportionate increase in the number of shares of authorized common stock.

headline: From Hermès Bags to Sally Hansen Nail Polish: The Art of Jacking Up Prices
summary: Companies try to charge more without tanking sales. “It will not be one-size-fits-all,” LVMH’s finance chief says.
